 more girls, cast magic on them, and play card battles with them! 🤫</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863310/extras/4d23f6e59728ebb893aaf6409f9697be.poster.avif?t=1776395768\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863310/extras/4d23f6e59728ebb893aaf6409f9697be.webm?t=1776395768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863310/extras/4d23f6e59728ebb893aaf6409f9697be.mp4?t=1776395768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >❣️Gameplay❣️</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players build decks in randomly generated maps and use cards to play against girls. Use different cards to choose different parts of the girls to cause damage. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863310/extras/184edce57369f5a6378ff81322e2a5fe.poster.avif?t=1776395768\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863310/extras/184edce57369f5a6378ff81322e2a5fe.webm?t=1776395768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863310/extras/184edce57369f5a6378ff81322e2a5fe.mp4?t=1776395768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >❣️Game Features❣️</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863310/extras/68ec735e15e3a7fb5772b2c61859ff02.avif?t=1776395768\" width=770 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 beautiful girls💋</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each of them has a unique charm. Explore their infinite possibilities and satisfy your every idea. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brand-new 3D graphics💥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring you an unparalleled visual feast! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamically changing maps🗺️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maps are randomly generated, and each experience is completely different. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random mysterious events🍷</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With many mysterious events, triggering plots or powerful cards? It all depends on your choice. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rich cards and combinations🎴</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable decks to form different strategies! More cards and dream stones allow you to create a more powerful deck. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two battle difficulties🍬</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want to experience the fun of card battles normally or beat the game, you can choose any one in the game. </p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>❗️Note❗️This game is a [General] version of other games, the content is the same, please do not purchase it again</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863310/extras/12336f418995d7930cedfc3acb904add.poster.avif?t=1776395768\" width=640 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863310/extras/12336f418995d7930cedfc3acb904add.webm?t=1776395768\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863310/extras/12336f418995d7930cedfc3acb904add.mp4?t=1776395768\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >❣️Background Story❣️</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist is a card player who has been single since birth, and only cares about playing cards. On his 30th birthday, he got a magi